  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK763">
<l>olittakkā leṉṉā muvari yelippakai</l>
<l>nāka muyirppak keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What if (a host of) hostile rats roar like the sea ? They will perish at the mere breath of the cobra.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
